text_answer.content: The pattern of the longest answer being the correct answer the majority of the time is what detracts from developing the skill of locating the main idea.  The focus is on detecting an established pattern.  A similar problem exists with the context clues since a student can determine the correct answer without using context.  As such, the question is not developing the ability to determine meaning through context.  I realize that the same part of speech may not appear in the stated paragraph.  That is why I am recommending a different approach to word study.
